Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Buying Judges and Acquiring a Patron Saint
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00sztqv
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 17 Mar 2000
Recalling a misleading first impression of America, Alistair Cook examines St. Patrick's Day celebrations and the influence of Irish immigrants on the Democratic Party.